WEBVTT

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:01.056
or by seeing further,

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:04.096
by standing on the shoulders of giants,

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:06.816
to paraphrase Newton.

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:10.456
The point is, scientists must be free

00:08:10.480 --> 00:08:14.496
to choose what they want to explore,

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:16.736
what they are passionate about

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:20.000
and they must be free
to report their findings.

00:08:21.200 --> 00:08:22.456
You heard me say

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:28.696
that respect for science
started to improve in Canada in 2015.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:30.736
How did we get here?